#5-text_indentation.txt
================================
How to use 5-text_indentation.py
================================

This library contains only one function, ``text_indenation()``
This function takes ``text`` as a parameter which should be a string

 ::

>>> t_ind = __import__('5-text_indentation').text_indentation
>>> t_ind('Hi. How are you?')
Hi.

How are you?

>>> t_ind(". , ? # :")
.

,?

# :
